- Why did you kill him?
- Don't kid yourself.

570
01:09:02.637 --> 01:09:06.431
- I just finished what you started.
- I didn't come here to kill.

571
01:09:06.432 --> 01:09:11.432
Then why did you come here?
For the money?

572
01:09:14.107 --> 01:09:16.400
