575
01:09:24.075 --> 01:09:28.537
(LAUGHS) You think
you can just quit?

576
01:09:28.538 --> 01:09:33.538
- (LAUGHS)
- What do you mean?

577
01:09:34.127 --> 01:09:39.127
I'll see you in three days.

578
01:09:41.384 --> 01:09:46.384
