591
01:12:06.737 --> 01:12:11.737
- It'll be all right. Okay?
- Okay.

592
01:12:22.295 --> 01:12:22.907
Let's go.

593
01:12:43.399 --> 01:12:45.984
(PHONE RINGING)

594
01:12:45.985 --> 01:12:47.277
